title: Khloe Kardashian flaunts her boobs making fans green with envy in plunging emerald dress after fuelling engagement rumours
text:
Khloe Kardashian flaunts her boobs making fans green with envy in plunging emerald dress after fuelling engagement rumours The star showed off her incredible figure in an emerald green dress   
Khloe Kardashian stepped outside her usual black and denim comfort zone for her latest photo shoot â€“ and she left fans green with envy over her incredible figure. 
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star wore an emerald green dress that plunged with a low V-neckline to show off her cleavage. 
The tight bodycon dress nipped in the 32-year-old's waist and flaunted her enviable curves. 
Khloe wore nude court shoes with the jewel ensemble. Khloe Kardashian flaunted her figure in an incredible green dress (Photo: Instagram) 
She wore her long blonde hair in loose beachy waves. 
She added another pop of colour with a slick of orange-red lipstick. 
And fans were quick to praised the reality star for her "flawless" look. 
"Looking fabulous," one fan commented. 
"Goddess you look amazing," another added. Khloe got ready for her close-up (Photo: Instagram) 
Earlier this week, Khloe added fuel to the fire of engagement rumours after stepping out with a huge rock on her wedding ring finger. 
She went for a date night with her man Tristan Thompson over the weekend as they enjoyed dinner at Ruth's Chris Steak House in Beverly Hills after his team the Cleveland Cavaliers lost to the Los Angeles Clippers. 
Whilst the basketball player was no doubt disappointed, what really becamee the talking point was Khloe's impressive diamond jewellery. Khloe Kardashian was wearing the impressive jewellery (Photo: WENN.com) 
The ring on her left hand was visible as she sat at court side for the game, prompting more speculation that the two lovebirds could be ready to take the next step. 
A later post on Snapchat showed that what appeared to be one massive rock was actually three identical rings. It was actually three smaller rings (Photo: Instagram/khloesnapchats) It's prompted more speculation (Photo: WENN.com) 
Earlier this month, a source told Entertainment Tonight: "There could be an engagement this summer." 
However, it was also claimed that marriage isn't Khloe's main focus right now. She was joined by her family to watch her man in action (Photo: WENN.com) 
"She's already done the marriage thing," the source added. "Getting engaged is not something she's sitting around stressing about. 
"If it happens, it happens, but it's not something she's stressing about right now." Like us on Facebook
